.PP
On \fIselect\fR systems, if the option \fI{otp, select_read}\fR is set, \fI{select_read, {SelectInfo, Data}}\fR is returned instead of \fI{ok, Data}\fR and a new asynchronous receive operation has been initiated, which can be seen as an automatic nowait call whenever a receive operation is completed.


